reviewText: My girlfriend didn't get to go to a local concert in town and was bummed out, so I got this to cheer her up. Most of the other concerts on Blu-Ray are a total rip off in price, this was one of the cheaper ones and other reviewers said these guys were entertaining. I actually did think it was pretty entertaining, and it was a cool experience to watch with my girlfriend with surround sound because it's pretty damn close to feeling like your at an actual live show. If you don't want to spend a lot of money and wanted to get a concert experience and be entertained, I think this purchase is worth the ten bucks.
summary: And I didn't even really like this band, but now I do
